data.description: Welcome to 4253 Fleet Dancer! Boasting an open floor plan, this residence perfectly blends functionality and style. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and an open floor plan. The primary bedroom features a sizable space and a walk-in closet. Downstairs, the living area is open with an inviting atmosphere for gatherings and entertaining. This home is conveniently located near shopping & 95 freeway. Enjoy the backyard with shade sail, turf, and low-maintenance finishes. Water Heater is 2 years old, owned alarm system and all appliances convey.
